MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2018-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 17th October, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 17th October,
2018, Shri M. J. Akbar relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of External Affairs.
